        <abstract>
            <p>Sends publications.</p>
            <p>Discusses comparative anatomy and evolutionary implications of several ligaments.</p>
            <p>Thinks effects of Chinese foot-binding are inherited.</p> 
<p>Criticises article on Darwinism in <hi rend="italic">Brockhaus’ Lexikon</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Mentions forthcoming book on mammalian vertebrae.</p>
        </abstract>
